# Gluestack UI v4

## Read first

1. `.agents/skills/gluestack-ui-v4/SKILL.md` (+ sub-skills: setup, components, styling, variants)
2. `.agents/skills/quoteflow/SKILL.md` - this repo’s web forks and layout gotchas
3. Docs: https://v4.gluestack.io/ui/docs/home/getting-started/installation

Install/refresh skills: `pnpm skills:install`

## Architecture

- All UI in `packages/ui` - screens, forms, Gluestack components
- `apps/web` - thin Next.js routes only
- Add components: `pnpm ui:add <name>` from repo root
- Config: `gluestack-ui.config.json`

## Styling rules

- Gluestack components over raw RN primitives
- Prefer props (`variant`, `size`, `space`) over redundant `className`
- **Semantic tokens only**: `text-foreground`, `bg-primary`, `border-border` - no `gray-500`, `red-600`
- Screens → `packages/ui/src/screens/`, not `apps/web/components`

## Web (Next.js)

- Run with **webpack**: `pnpm dev:web` (`next dev --webpack`)
- Many primitives have `index.web.tsx` - HTML elements, not RN
- Strip RN-only props before DOM spread (`multiline`, `onPress`, etc.)
- **`Box` is `flex-col`** - add `flex-row` for horizontal layouts
- Theme vars in `globals.css` **and** `config.ts` (SSR / no FOUC)

## v4 only

Use v4 CLI/docs for this project. Do not migrate to v5 unless explicitly requested.
